#

Carrot Ginger Soup

40 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegangluten-freedairy-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

souphealthyeasy

Description

A warm and comforting soup that balances the sweetness of carrots with the zing of fresh ginger.

Ingredients

  • carrots: 4 cups, chopped
  • onion: 1, diced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • fresh ginger: 1 tablespoon, grated
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • coconut milk: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
